---
---
<section class="relative min-h-screen w-full pt-20 overflow-hidden bg-white">
  <!-- Subtle patterns -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0 opacity-[0.03]" style="background-image: radial-gradient(#0EA5E9 1px, transparent 1px); background-size: 40px 40px;"></div>

  <div class="relative z-10 mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-8 py-24 lg:py-32">
    <div class="grid gap-16 lg:grid-cols-2 lg:items-center">
      <div class="reveal">
        <div class="mb-8 inline-flex items-center gap-3 rounded-full bg-blue-50 px-4 py-2 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-[#0EA5E9]">
          <span class="flex h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-[#0EA5E9] animate-pulse"></span>
          Referência em Medicina Estética
        </div>
        
        <h1 class="text-6xl font-extrabold leading-[1] text-[#0F172A] sm:text-8xl uppercase tracking-tighter">
          A Ciência da <br />
          <span class="text-[#0EA5E9]">Beleza Real</span>
        </h1>
        
        <p class="mt-10 max-w-lg text-xl leading-relaxed text-slate-500 font-medium">
          Onde a alta tecnologia encontra o cuidado médico especializado. Protocolos personalizados para realçar sua essência com naturalidade e segurança.
        </p>
        
        <div class="mt-14 flex flex-col gap-6 sm:flex-row">
          <a href="#contato" class="btn-medical px-10">
            Agendar Avaliação
          </a>
          <a href="#tratamentos" class="btn-outline-medical px-10">
            Ver Tratamentos
          </a>
        </div>
        
        <div class="mt-16 flex items-center gap-12 text-slate-300">
          <div class="text-center">
            <span class="block text-3xl font-black text-[#0F172A]">15+</span>
            <span class="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest font-bold">Anos de Experiência</span>
          </div>
          <div class="h-10 w-px bg-slate-100"></div>
          <div class="text-center">
            <span class="block text-3xl font-black text-[#0F172A]">10k+</span>
            <span class="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest font-bold">Vidas Transformadas</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="reveal relative lg:ml-auto w-full max-w-xl">
        <div class="relative z-10 overflow-hidden rounded-3xl shadow-2xl border-4 border-white shadow-blue-500/10">
          <img 
            src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1576091160550-2173dba999ef?auto=format&fit=crop&q=80&w=1200" 
            alt="Atendimento Médico Premium" 
            class="h-full w-full object-cover grayscale-[20%] hover:grayscale-0 transition-all duration-1000"
          />
        </div>
        <!-- Decorative elements -->
        <div class="absolute -right-12 -top-12 h-64 w-64 rounded-full bg-blue-100/50 blur-3xl"></div>
        <div class="absolute -left-12 -bottom-12 h-64 w-64 rounded-full bg-blue-100/50 blur-3xl"></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
